{"tid":2392143,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"希特拉坐過廁板拍賣　料成交價接近16萬","createTime":"2021-02-02T15:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T03:12:59.000Z","uid":81228,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4d08a31af049cbd6a7a73c10ef2298310062fb12","tid":2392143,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/2/1612171321_cL-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F2%2F1612171321_cL-1280w.jpg&h=72e6fac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/2/1612171323_dN-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F2%2F1612171323_dN-1280w.jpg&h=dcb5a1b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/2/1612171325_rJ-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F2%2F1612171325_rJ-1280w.jpg&h=04b5d217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這可說是二戰最古怪的戰利品──納粹德國領袖希特拉坐過的廁板，而且還將會拍賣，料成交價可達1.5萬英鎊(約15.9萬港元)。<br />\n<br />\n希特拉坐過的廁板來自其貝希特斯加登別墅的私人浴室，是美國士兵Ragnvald Borch的戰利品。別墅在二戰結束前被轟炸嚴重損毀，上級軍官叫他們「喜歡甚麼便拿去」，當年另一名士兵也有問Borch為甚麼拿廁板，他回答：「你認為希特拉會將自己屁股放在哪裡？」Borch將廁板運回新澤西的住所，將它擺放在地牢裡「展出」。他的家人下周在馬里蘭州舉行拍賣會，料成交價介乎1至1.5萬英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%8D%A8%E8%A3%81%E5%B8%8C%E9%AD%94%EF%BD%9C%E5%B8%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%8B%89%E5%9D%90%E9%81%8E%E5%BB%81%E6%9D%BF%E6%8B%8D%E8%B3%A3-%E6%96%99%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%83%B9%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%9116%E8%90%AC-254183\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E7%258D%25A8%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25B8%258C%25E9%25AD%2594%25EF%25BD%259C%25E5%25B8%258C%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%259D%2590%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BB%2581%25E6%259D%25BF%25E6%258B%258D%25E8%25B3%25A3-%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%258E%25A5%25E8%25BF%259116%25E8%2590%25AC-254183&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=52ce89a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%8D%A8%E8%A3%81%E5%B8%8C%E9%AD%94%EF%BD%9C%E5%B8%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%8B%89%E5%9D%90%E9%81%8E%E5%BB%81%E6%9D%BF%E6%8B%8D%E8%B3%A3-%E6%96%99%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%83%B9%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%9116%E8%90%AC-254183</a>"},{"pid":"9210d11a23a951ed95af59481c36e465d50b82d9","tid":2392143,"uid":301989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"有冇hitler啲屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a895248a80a49ea43584aebd1b1dfc82d1919445","tid":2392143,"uid":28547,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"蠢<br />\n攞隻錶既話條錶帶都唔止"},{"pid":"a45bb10b87d9da5e4afb2f2691e15a4c07c3d55b","tid":2392143,"uid":324041,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"個美軍會唔會攞錯咗希特拉工人房個厠所果塊廁所板咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0622c22ab8add7c801afbb2d0d7e39c5a04001b","tid":2392143,"uid":147029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"睇錯希拉莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}